headline: Corpay to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Results on February 4, 2026
summary: ATLANTA, January 21, 2026--Corpay, Inc., (NYSE: CPAY) the corporate payments company, today announced that the Company will host a conference call to discuss fourth quarter and fiscal year 2025 financial results on Wednesday, February 4, 2026 at 5:30 pm ET. Hosting the call will be Ron Clarke, Chief Executive Officer, Peter Walker, Chief Financial Officer and Jim Eglseder, Investor Relations. headline: Why Corpay (CPAY) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of business payments company Corpay (NYSE:CPAY) jumped 2.9% in the afternoon session after Jefferies raised its price target on the stock to $370 from $335 while maintaining its Buy rating.
